<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>يعوده.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فما تحوَّز له عن فراشه <span class="c1">"<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قال:</span> قوله: "تحوَّز " هو التَّنحِّى.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وفيه لغتان:</span> التحَّوُّز، والتَّحيُّز.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>